  description: |
    Runtime-local pricing workflow that invokes WASM, native-code, and sidecar
    handler paths. The live smoke registers a real sidecar process and lets
    WASM/native fall back to explicit runtime stubs unless binaries are
    provided by the operator artifact harness.
  dialect: vflow
  tags: [example, p0, artifacts, wasm, native, sidecar]

spec:
  activities:
    - id: trigger
