  name: "Fastpath V-Rule Risk Scoring (gRPC)"
  description: |
    Apple-to-apple comparator for `047-fastpath-vrule-risk-scoring`,
    over gRPC instead of HTTP webhook, on the **fastpath runtime**.
    Same V-Rule pack (`fastpath_risk_v1`), same six input fields,
    equivalent decision shape — isolates pure protocol overhead
    (gRPC vs HTTP) on the fastpath kernel-state-machine-bypassed
    path.

    Activities (4): Trigger(grpc) → VRule → EndTrigger → End. Same
