    `ProtoHandle` directly into the fastpath inline executor — no
    kernel state-machine overhead. V-Rule fastpath dispatch detects
    the proto handle and takes the proto-native input + output path
    inherited from Phases 2 and 3 of the devplan. The same compiled
    V-Rule pack (`fastpath_risk_v1`) drives both 047 (JSON in/out)
    and 061 (proto in/out).

    For the standard-runtime variant (apple-to-apple with 049
    webhook standard) see `060-standard-vrule-risk-scoring-grpc`.

  dialect: vflow
  tags: [example, p0, grpc, vrule, risk-scoring, bench, fastpath]

spec:
  activities:
    - id: trigger
      activity_type: Trigger
      trigger_config:
